Class MsgLineImpl

java.lang.Object
us.mn.state.dot.tms.server.BaseObjectImpl
us.mn.state.dot.tms.server.MsgLineImpl
All Implemented Interfaces:
SonarObject, MsgLine, Storable
public class MsgLineImpl extends BaseObjectImpl implements MsgLine
A message line contains the properties of a single line MULTI string for filling in a message pattern.
Author:
Douglas Lau
